/14964780/files/collection-v2025-03-04.zip/content"}}], "swh": null, "owners": [{"id": "15218"}], "status": "published", "stats": {"downloads": 22, "unique_downloads": 21, "views": 78, "unique_views": 73, "version_downloads": 22, "version_unique_downloads": 21, "version_unique_views": 73, "version_views": 78}, "state": "done", "submitted": true}, {"created": "2016-05-18T15:17:51+00:00", "modified": "2020-01-24T19:22:43.056089+00:00", "id": 51284, "conceptrecid": "633421", "doi": "10.5281/zenodo.51284", "conceptdoi": "", "doi_url": "https://doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.51284", "metadata": {"title": "MoMA Collection - Automatic Monthly Update", "doi": "10.5281/zenodo.51284", "publication_date": "2016-05-10", "description": "<p>The Artworks dataset contains {artworks count}&nbsp;records, representing all of the works that have been accessioned into MoMA&rsquo;s collection and cataloged in our database. It includes basic metadata for each work, including title, artist, date made, medium, dimensions, and date acquired by the Museum. Some of these records have incomplete information and are noted as &ldquo;not Curator Approved.&rdquo; The Artists dataset contains {artists count} records, representing all the artists who have work in MoMA&#39;s collection and have been cataloged in our database. It includes basic metadata for each artist, including name, nationality, gender (labeled &quot;code&quot;), birth year, death year, Wiki QID, and Getty ULAN ID.</p>", "access_right": "open", "creators": [{"name": "Robot, Open Data", "affiliation": "The Museum of Modern Art (MoMA)"}], "related_identifiers": [{"identifier": "10.5281/zenodo.45881", "relation": "isPreviousVersionOf", "scheme": "doi"}, {"identifier": "10.5281/zenodo.46902", "relation": "isPreviousVersionOf", "scheme": "doi"}, {"identifier": "https =>//github.com/MuseumofModernArt/collection/tree/v1.5", "relation": "isSupplementedBy", "scheme": "handle"}], "resource_type": {"title": "Dataset", "type": "dataset"}, "license": {"